These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, skateboarding, biathlon, soccer, climbing, badminton
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, tea, soy-milk, sprite, milk, 7up
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person drinking milk##6
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking mirinda##7
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking tea##7
10. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
11. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
13. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
14. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
15. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Sport          | skateboarding    | baseball    | parkour | climbing | biathlon | soccer    | badminton |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee | tea  | milk   | soy-milk    | mirinda | 7up |

