.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, dressmaker, doctor, entrepreneur, lawyer, musician, nurse
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, december, may, october, july, april, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the nurse and the dressmaker##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the entrepreneur##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the musician##1
 5. the engineer is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 6. the musician is somewhere between the entrepreneur and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 7. the lawyer is somewhere between the entrepreneur and the dressmaker##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
10. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
11. the person who's birthday is in april is not the nurse##6
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in october and the entrepreneur##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Job    | nurse  | doctor | musician | entrepreneur | engineer     | lawyer | dressmaker  |
| Birthday   | may | april | december  | february  | july | october      | november |

