 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the airplane##7
10. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
11. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person driving the train##6
13. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in february##7
14. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
16. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person driving the boat##6
17. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
18. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
19. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

