 5. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 6. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
 8. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 9. the colonial house is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
10. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
11. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
12. the person traveling to miami is the wooden house##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
14. the person traveling to london is the farmhouse house##1
15. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
16. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

