 3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching epic movies##7
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is the fan salsa##1
 7. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
 8. the fan gospel is not the person watching spy movies##6
 9. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the fan salsa##5
10. the fan disco is not the person watching spy movies##6
11. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
12. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan d&b##3
13. the person watching epic movies is not the fan indie##6
14. the person watching musical movies is the fan disco##1
15. the fan indie is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
16. the fan folk is on the left of the fan d&b##1
17. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3    |    4    |      5       |    6     |     7      |
